For this task, I created an infographic using Canva. I chose Canva because it is simple to use and provides many templates which helped me design easily.

My infographic explains the concept of digital literacy and why it is important for students. I included topics such as the meaning of digital literacy, useful digital tools like Google Docs, GitHub, and LinkedIn, and safe internet practices. The design is simple and easy to understand so that anyone can quickly learn from it.

One interesting thing I found was how quickly a professional-looking design can be created using Canva. At first, I found it slightly difficult to choose the right layout and colors, but after trying different options, I was able to create a clean design.

This task helped me understand how to present information visually in a simple and effective way.
